## Architectural Patterns

### Pattern 1: Layered Architecture

**Structure:**
```
src/
 controllers/     # Handle HTTP requests/responses
 services/        # Business logic
 repositories/    # Data access layer
 models/          # Data models
 middleware/      # Express/Fastify middleware
